{
  "stem": "18770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're making their first steps to round them up, I guess, to put them in a controlled ghetto or wherever they're going to put them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this man has to make a choice as to whether he's gonna take us to the destination he's promised to take us to or whether he's just going to say, sorry folks, I got to go back.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he takes us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's-- the whole journey was like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Very existential.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In any moment, you could be discovered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could be caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A guy could leave you in the lurch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of them killed later by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think in, I think in a place like Chelm, probably 98% of the Jews who lived there were exterminated by the Nazis later on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We go very briefly to Lwow-- to my father's hometown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not sure why we go there, but I do know that his side of the family represent those people who I said before who decide that they're going to stay put.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That they are, they're not going to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That they-- and so they, they remain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we continue on, and we go to Vilno-- Vilnius, as the Lithuanians call it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The capital of Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What has been happening is that Poland and Lithuania are being divided in the seesaw between Russia and Germany, who-- at that point, Hitler and Stalin have a pact.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So even while we were in Poland, in Chelm, my, my memory is that the Poles evacuated-- or the army withdrew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans come in briefly, then the Russians come in briefly-- not because they are fighting each other, but because they take their territory.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the Germans come back to stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
